FuncDef: This command specifies the range of indexes used by SR OS to automatically assign an index to ETH-CFM domains that are created in model-driven interfaces without an index explicitly specified by the user or client.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the lower value of the index range. The value must be less than or equal to the end value. Values-1 to 4294967295.
Specifies the upper value of the index range. The value must be greater than or equal to the start value. Values-1 to 4294967295.
